;An Important Change in Firefox: Dedicated Profiles
Un importante cambiamento in Firefox: le profilos dedicate


;What’s Changed
Lo que es cambiate


;Before, all Firefox installations were sharing a single profile by default. Now, Firefox provides dedicated profiles for each Firefox installation (this includes installations of Firefox Nightly, Firefox Beta, or Firefox ESR). This will make Firefox more stable when switching between Firefox installations on the same computer.
Antea, tote le installationes de Firefox compartiva de ordinario un sol profilo. Ora, Firefox forni profilos dedicate pro cata installation de Firefox (isto include installationes de Firefox Nightly, Firefox Beta, o Firefox ESR). Isto rendera Firefox plus stabile quando illo commuta inter installationes de Firefox sur le mesme computator.


;How Dedicated Profiles Work
Como functiona le profilos dedicate


;Firefox saves information such as bookmarks, passwords and user preferences in a set of files called your profile. This profile is stored in a separate location from the Firefox program files.
Firefox salva informationes tal como marcapaginas, contrasignos e optiones de usator in un collection de files appellate: tu profilo. Iste profilo es servate in un position separate ab le files de programma de Firefox.


;The installation you choose as your primary Firefox installation will keep your previously shared profile data like bookmarks, history and passwords.
Le installation que tu elige como tu installation de Firefox primari retenera tu datos de profilo previemente compartite como: marcapaginas, chronologia e contrasignos.


;You have not lost any personal data or customizations. Any previous profile data is safe and attached to the first Firefox installation that was opened after this change.
Tu non ha perdite ulle tu datos o personalisationes. Ulle previe datos de profilo es secur e attachate al prime installation de Firefox que esseva aperite post iste cambiamento.


;All of your Firefox installations will now have separate profiles.
Tote tu installationes de Firefox habera ora profilos separate.


;What You Need to Do
Lo que tu debe facer


;If you do nothing, each installation will have a separate profile. This means your profile data will be different on each installation of Firefox.
Si tu face nihil, cata installation habera un profilo separate. Isto significa que le datos de tu profilo sera differente sur cata installation de Firefox.


;You can change which installation uses which profile using the profile manager. Directions on how to use the profile manager are available on <a href="%(support)s">this support page</a>.
Tu pote cambiar per le gestor de profilo qual profilo usa cata installation. Le directiones sur como usar le gestor de profilo es disponibile sur <a href="%(support)s">iste pagina de supporto</a>.


;While profiles are now connected to each installation of Firefox, you can use your Firefox Account to keep them in sync. If you would like all of your profile data to be the same on all installations of Firefox, we recommend you sync all of your profiles with a Firefox Account.
Durante que le profilos es ora connectite a cata installation de Firefox, tu pote usar tu conto de Firefox pro los mantener synchronisate. Si tu desira que tote le datos de tu profilo sia le mesme sur tote le installationes de Firefox, nos recommenda que tu synchronisa tote tu profilos con un sol conto de Firefox.


;A Firefox Account is the easiest way to make your profiles consistent on all of your versions of Firefox. You also get additional benefits like sending tabs and secure password storage.
Un conto de Firefox es le maniera plus facile pro render consistente tu profilos sur tote tu versiones de Firefox. Tu obtene alsi altere beneficios como: invio de schedas e immagazinage de contrasigno secur.


;You’re signed in and ready to start using Sync.
Tu es connexe e preste a initiar a usar Sync.


